data.description:
Discover the ideal home! Nestled on a tranquil cul-de-sac, this 3-bedroom, 3-bathroom residence combines convenience with comfort. Situated on 1.5 acres, it offers both space and intimacy. Step onto the front covered porch for serene morning coffees, or retreat to the covered back deck overlooking the fenced yard. With a two-car garage, entry through the expansive laundry room showcases granite countertops matching the kitchen.

Inside, the kitchen boasts modern appliances, abundant cabinet space, and a seamless flow into the living area and breakfast nook, adorned with a charming bay window. Enjoy the spacious living room featuring a fireplace and ample natural light. Welcoming formal living and dining rooms greet guests upon entry.

Down the hall, discover a generous bathroom with ample storage and a tub/shower combo. Bedroom 1 offers comfort with a sizable closet, while a versatile bonus room awaits, perfect for an office, gym, or additional bedroom. The main bedroom, at the end of the hall, impresses with an en suite featuring a water closet, expansive counter space, stand-up shower, and an oversized walk-in closet.

Adjacent to the kitchen, another sizable bedroom awaits, complete with an en suite. Adorned with beautiful wood flooring throughout the main areas, the home boasts a new roof installed in 2019. Seize the opportunity to transform this residence into your personal sanctuary!
